ました</p></div><p class="jsx-7fa9a78cf9e40b90 linkButton"><a href="https://kakuyomu.jp/maho" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="jsx-1174100236 Link"><span class="jsx-1696363835 ButtonStyles primary shrink "><span class="jsx-1696363835"><span class="jsx-7fa9a78cf9e40b90 text"><svg width="106" height="20" viewBox="0 0 106 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g><path d="M19.1915 0.0688477H1.90088C1.17169 0.0688477 0.580566 0.659972 0.580566 1.38916V18.6798C0.580566 19.409 1.17169 20.0001 1.90088 20.0001H19.1915C19.9207 20.0001 20.5118 19.409 20.5118 18.6798V1.38916C20.5118 0.659972 19.9207 0.0688477 19.1915 0.0688477Z" fill="white"></path><path d="M5.78742 13.1756H4.2168V3.70508H8.70311V5.27845H5.78742V13.1756Z" fill="#222222"></path><path d="M16.878 16.3665H12.7163V14.7931H15.3047V6.896H16.878V16.3665Z" fill="#222222"></path><path d="M42.0275 4.28002C40.9657 4.30752 39.4198 4.39829 37.3183 4.62385C37.5412 3.25402 37.6044 2.06299 37.6044 1.18553V1.11401L35.7477 0L34.796 1.58713L35.7642 2.16751C35.745 2.66538 35.6762 3.62536 35.4342 4.8494C33.9736 5.03645 32.3122 5.2785 30.4115 5.59758L28.8298 4.71187L27.9249 6.3265L30.0786 7.53129L30.1226 7.52304C30.1639 7.51478 32.2984 7.1517 34.939 6.79686C33.88 10.2187 31.476 14.6197 26.0132 17.3979L25.9004 17.4556L26.7338 19.1088L26.8494 19.0483C33.2116 15.731 35.8578 10.6725 36.9223 6.5438C38.5781 6.34851 40.2726 6.18622 41.6809 6.13671C42.2145 6.13671 42.2063 6.22748 42.1953 6.58781C41.7414 12.1799 39.882 14.2016 39.1008 14.5702C38.9742 14.2539 38.5534 13.4287 37.3541 12.5952L37.2468 12.521L36.2098 14.0696L36.3309 14.1356C37.2001 14.6087 37.5274 15.6017 37.6484 16.1876C37.7227 16.5232 37.9675 16.779 38.4296 16.7377C42.6849 16.2151 43.7796 10.0014 44.0602 6.56581C44.1345 5.22074 43.8622 4.27452 42.0302 4.28002H42.0275Z" fill="white"></path><path d="M49.7377 11.594C53.6518 8.42795 55.9844 5.16843 56.672 1.90615L56.7216 1.6806L54.455 0.321777L53.5033 1.9089L54.587 2.55806C54.2075 3.74084 52.8926 6.65928 48.5741 10.15